{"title":"BikeRadar Podcast | 10 bits of kit to get through winter","link":"https://www.bikeradar.com/news/bikeradar-podcast-winter-mtb-kit/","date":1613408408000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><section itemprop=\"articleBody\"><p>Though winter might be coming to an end soon, it has been a long one in the UK. However, Tom and Alex have found it a little more comfortable thanks to some key pieces of kit.</p><p>In this episode of the BikeRadar Podcast, they talk through the kit that has helped make their winters a little more comfortable than they might otherwise have been.</p><p>Don’t forget to subscribe to the BikeRadar Podcast&nbsp;via&nbsp;<a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/gb/podcast/the-bikeradar-podcast/id1461106709\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Apple</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/6aLvE13Bge7WC7AWbiR3LS\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Spotify,</a> or just search for us on your preferred podcast provider.</p><p>Each of the items mentioned in the podcast are also listed below…</p><h2>Alex’s picks</h2><h3>Sealskinz socks</h3><div><picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/01/Sealskinz-socks-2-e10a3c0.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=299%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/01/Sealskinz-socks-2-e10a3c0.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=599%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/01/Sealskinz-socks-2-e10a3c0.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=899%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/01/Sealskinz-socks-2-e10a3c0.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1199%2C799 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/01/Sealskinz-socks-2-e10a3c0.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=299%2C199, https://im